s0 ws0">ble correspondence courses and four </div><div class="t mff x1 h2a ye3 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sets of Sabbath School lessons. He </div><div class="t m100 x1 h2a ye4 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and his wife, Betty, have three adult </div><div class="t m101 x1 h2a ye5 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">children. His hobbies include garden-</div><div class="t m102 x1 h2a ye6 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing, cooking and writing. </div><div class="t m103 x12 h2b ye7 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Watch at your local Adventist Book </div><div class="t m104 x1 h2b ye8 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Center for the supplementary book. It </div><div class="t m105 x1 h2b y3c ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is written by W R. </div><div class="t m106 x1d h2a y36 ff7 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">L. </div><div class="t m107 x23 h2b y3c ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scragg and is </div><div class="t m108 x1 h2b ye9 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">being published by the Review and </div><div class="t m2a x1 h2b yea ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Herald Publishing Association. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
